  <p class="">The grill is hot, the sands are hot, and ‚Äì most important of all ‚Äì your worlds and avatars are <em>hot</em>.</p><p class="">Your Summer Music Festival Jam winners are here! As always, we‚Äôre blown away by the skill of our creative community, who have brought out their absolute best to celebrate summer vibes.</p><p class="">As a reminder, the Summer Music Festival Jam was open to world and avatar creators, encouraging both to create content that was season-appropriate, full of vibes, and accessible to our entire community. If you‚Äôd like to see the full details, you can check out the original blog post <a href="https://hello.vrchat.com/blog/summer-music-jam"><span>here</span></a>!</p><p class="">Enough stalling ‚Äì let‚Äôs get into the winners!</p><h3><strong>World Selections</strong></h3><p class="">Worlds were judged based on a few categories:</p><ul data-rte-list="default"><li><p class="">Summer Vibe-iness</p></li><li><p class="">Media Player Integration</p></li><li><p class="">Performance Level</p></li><li><p class="">Ease of Use</p></li></ul><p class="">Given that, here are our selections:</p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
