  <p class="">In honor of Gold, we have placed a golden flower vase in the VRChat Home. This vase serves as a symbol of his enduring presence and the warmth he brought to our community. We invite you to visit this memorial and reflect on the cherished memories and lasting impact Gold has left behind.</p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
