  <p class="">We will be sharing more on January 18th, however ‚Äì you can expect a Developer Update to be released then where we‚Äôll discuss some of the cool things coming next for the Creator Economy!</p><h3>A Thanks to Our Community</h3><p class="">We're beyond excited to see the creative wonders you'll unleash with these new tools. Stay tuned for more updates, and as always, thank you for loving VRChat as much as we do.</p><p class="">We‚Äôll see you next time!</p>





















  
  



