  <p class="">For press or media inquiries, please contact <a href="mailto:press@vrchat.com">press@vrchat.com</a></p><p class="">We‚Äôre hiring! <a href="https://hello.vrchat.com/careers">Check out  open positions on our site</a></p>]]></description><media:content type="image/png" url="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5f0770791aaf57311515b23d/1700608585040-WV8YP1M18U22QDMZDD5K/BlogHeroImage.png?format=1500w" medium="image" isDefault="true" width="1500" height="844"><media:title type="plain">Paid Subscriptions: Now in Open Beta!</media:title></media:content></item><item><title>Introducing Content Gating</title><dc:creator>Tupper</dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 19 Sep 2023 21:25:53 +0000</pubDate><link>https://hello.vrchat.com/blog/content-gating</link><guid isPermaLink="false">5f0770791aaf57311515b23d:61e9ceaed5e64e33580b3b7e:650860b1fd4f6c5ab045902c</guid><description><![CDATA[<figure class="
