  <p class="">For press or media inquiries, please contact <a href="mailto:press@vrchat.com">press@vrchat.com</a></p><p class="">We‚Äôre hiring! <a href="https://hello.vrchat.com/careers">Check out  open positions on our site</a></p>]]></description><media:content type="image/png" url="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5f0770791aaf57311515b23d/1695074397324-9G3FLH6NZAK4NBDSLLSX/KeyArt_Spookality_2023_V3_SaveTheDate.png?format=1500w" medium="image" isDefault="true" width="1500" height="844"><media:title type="plain">Spookality 2023 is Coming Soon!</media:title></media:content></item><item><title>VRChat Mobile Beta Now Live!</title><dc:creator>Tupper</dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 17 Aug 2023 22:12:32 +0000</pubDate><link>https://hello.vrchat.com/blog/mobile-alpha-now-live</link><guid isPermaLink="false">5f0770791aaf57311515b23d:61e9ceaed5e64e33580b3b7e:64d3e6b24cc8dd66cad1073b</guid><description><![CDATA[<iframe scrolling="no" allowfullscreen src="//www.youtube.com/embed/YpyMVAcllYs?wmode=opaque" width="854" frameborder="0" height="480"></iframe>




  <p class=""><span>We‚Äôre excited to announce that the VRChat Mobile Alpha has begun! This is a big moment for us ‚Äì and we‚Äôre excited to give our users the ability to take VRChat with them, wherever they happen to be going.</span></p><p class=""><span>Remember, <strong>this is an alpha</strong>! This is an opportunity for you to help our team test the mobile app across devices and in a variety of different environments. Your feedback will help us create a better overall experience for all users of VRChat. That also means that you should expect a few bugs, as well as a changing, ever-evolving experience as we continuously test what works best for mobile users.</span></p><p class=""><span><strong>So ‚Äì let‚Äôs jump right to it: how do you get into the alpha?</strong></span></p><p class=""><span>Provided your Android phone or tablet meets the minimum requirements (see below!) and that you have VRChat Plus, you can download the alpha right now from this link.</span></p><p class=""><strong>Hey! The VRChat Mobile Alpha‚Ä¶ is now the VRChat Mobile Beta! Ignore the above ‚Äî you no longer need VRChat Plus to access the Beta ‚Äî anyone can with an appropriate Android device!</strong></p><p class="">We know you probably have many more questions, though ‚Äì we‚Äôve gathered up what we imagine the most commonly asked ones will be, and we‚Äôll be answering them below. If your specific question isn‚Äôt on this list, we‚Äôd suggest checking out the relevant thread on the Ask forums and posting there!</p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
