  <h3><strong>When Will People See My Stuff?</strong></h3><p class="">This year, we want to ensure that all of our UFOlogists have enough time to properly examine whatever oddities they find in the wild. To make that happen, we‚Äôll be spotlighting worlds and avatars on a weekly basis. For worlds, this will mean adding them to the Spookality World Row. For avatars, it‚Äôll mean adding them into the Spookality Hub world.<br><br>While that means that early submissions will have the greatest chance of being seen by the most people, we‚Äôd encourage you not to rush!</p><p class="">The Spookality World Row will be active until a few weeks after Halloween. Likewise, the Spookality Hub won‚Äôt be going anywhere anytime soon.</p><h3><strong>Prepare For First Contact!</strong></h3><p class="">Creators, it‚Äôs time to start prepping your machinations!</p><p class="">Excited about what you‚Äôre working on? <a href="https://twitter.com/vrchat">Tweet at us</a> and use the hashtag #Spookality2022 ‚Äì if we‚Äôre sufficiently creeped out/in awe/[REDACTED], then we‚Äôll share your work!</p><p class="">Spookality is an exciting time in VRChat, and us Humans are just absolutely charmed by what your specie‚Äì er, what your‚Ä¶ uhh‚Ä¶ <em>talents</em>! What your talents have dreamed up! Good luck to all that enter!</p>





















  
  



